nodes.text: Bounty Hunters 16 is the upcoming sixteenth issue of the canon comic book series Star Wars: Bounty Hunters, and is part of the Star Wars: War of the Bounty Hunters event. It will be written by Ethan Sacks, illustrated by Paolo Villanelli, and published by Marvel Comics on September 22, 2021.
